fields.title: The Django Admin is Great

fields.content:
Welcome to the Django-Contenteditable demo site. Before you can edit anything, you'll need to log in (the link is in the upper left). The default login is admin/admin. If you don't log in, I hope you can read Italian.

If a piece of text is editable, you click on the 'EDIT' button next to it to initiate editing. To save, click the same button.

By the way, this block of text is an editable chunk. Go ahead and edit me!
